message.content: ∀ {p : ℕ} [hp : Fact p.Prime], p > 2 → ∀ {a b : ℕ}, a ≠ b → a < p → b < p → ¬p ∣ (∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * (a ^ i - b ^ i))
∀ {p : ℕ} [inst : Fact p.Prime], p ≠ 2 → ∀ {a b : ℕ}, a ≠ b → a < p → b < p → ¬(∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * a ^ i ≡ ∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * b ^ i [MOD p])
∀ {p : ℕ}, p ∈ {3, 5, 7, 11, ...} → ∀ {a b : ℕ}, a ≠ b → a ∈ Finset.range p → b ∈ Finset.range p → let F := λ n, ∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * n ^ i in ¬(F a - F b) % p = 0
∀ {p : ℕ} [hp : Fact p.Prime], p ≠ 2 → ∀ {a b : ℕ}, a ≠ b → a < p → b < p → ¬(∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * a ^ i) ≡ (∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * b ^ i) [ZMOD p]

∀ {p : ℕ} (hp : p.Prime) (hodd : p % 2 = 1) {a b : ℕ} (ha : a < p) (hb : b < p) (hab : a ≠ b),
  let F := λ n, ∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * n ^ i in
  ¬(F a ≡ F b [ZMOD p])
∀ {p : ℕ} [Fact (Nat.Prime p)] (hp : p ≠ 2) {a b : ℕ}, a ≠ b → a < p → b < p → ¬((∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * a ^ i) - (∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * b ^ i) ≡ 0 [ZMOD p])

∀ {p : ℕ} (hp : p.Prime) (hodd : p ≠ 2) {a b : ℕ}, a ≠ b → a < p → b < p →
  let F (n : ℕ) := ∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * n ^ i
  in ¬(F a ≡ F b [MOD p])

∀ {p : ℕ}, p ∈ {n | n.Prime ∧ n ≠ 2} →
  ∀ (a b : ℕ), a ∈ Finset.range p → b ∈ Finset.range p → a ≠ b →
    ¬(1 + 2 * a + 3 * a^2 + ∑ i in Finset.range (p - 2), (i + 3) * a^(i + 2) -
      (1 + 2 * b + 3 * b^2 + ∑ i in Finset.range (p - 2), (i + 3) * b^(i + 2)) ≡ 0 [ZMOD p])

∀ {p : ℕ} [hp : Fact (Nat.Prime p)], p > 2 →
  ∀ {a b : ℤ}, a ∈ Finset.range p → b ∈ Finset.range p → a ≠ b →
    let F (n : ℤ) := ∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * n ^ i 
    in (F a - F b) % ↑p ≠ 0
∀ {p : ℕ} [Fact p.Prime], p ≠ 2 → ∀ {a b : ℕ}, a ≠ b → a < p → b < p → ¬ (∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * (a ^ i) - (i + 1) * (b ^ i) : ℕ) % p = 0
